{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N002234", "chronotag": "1739874550054", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CF2234", "numeroOrdreDepot": "2234", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0324", "triAmendement": "afoaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaabozs", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795998", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845514", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;K/Bidi"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "\u00c9TAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 42", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 42", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 42", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0324C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "VA", "libelleMission": "Coh\u00e9sion des territoires", "missionRef": "2850"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "H\u00e9bergement, parcours vers le logement et insertion des personnes vuln\u00e9rables", "programmeRef": "461654", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Aide \u00e0 l'acc\u00e8s au logement", "programmeRef": "461656", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Urbanisme, territoires et am\u00e9lioration de l'habitat", "programmeRef": "461658", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Impulsion et coordination de la politique d'am\u00e9nagement du territoire", "programmeRef": "461660", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Politique de la ville", "programmeRef": "461662", "autorisationEngagement": "0", "creditPaiement": "0", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Interventions territoriales de l'\u00c9tat", "programmeRef": "461664", "autorisationEngagement": "-50000000", "creditPaiement": "-50000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "R\u00e9habilitation des logements anciens en Outremer", "programmeRef": "461666", "autorisationEngagement": "50000000", "creditPaiement": "50000000", "action": "cr\u00e9ation", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Cet amendement cre&#x0301;e le programme &#x00AB; Re&#x0301;habilitation des logements anciens en Outremer &#x00BB; et l&#x2019;abonde de 50 000 000 &#x20AC; en AE et CP provenant de l&#x2019;action 02 &#x00AB; Eau &#x2013; Agriculture en Bretagne &#x00BB; hors titre II du programme 162 &#x00AB;Intervention territoriales de l&#x2019;Etat &#x00BB;. Ce nouveau programme est destine&#x0301; a&#x0300; allouer un budget spe&#x0301;cifique a&#x0300; la re&#x0301;novation des habitats anciens dans les territoires dits d&#x2019;Outremer de l&#x2019;article 73 de la Constitution.</p><p>Le logement en Outremer est un enjeu majeur. Dans certains territoires, comme a&#x0300; la Re&#x0301;union, le manque de logement atteint des niveaux records et la construction de logements neufs est en forte baisse.</p><p>De&#x0300;s lors, il convient de promouvoir et soutenir tout projet de re&#x0301;habilitation du ba&#x0302;ti ancien destine&#x0301; a&#x0300; la cre&#x0301;ation de logements. C&#x2019;est l&#x2019;objectif du pre&#x0301;sent amendement.</p><p>En cre&#x0301;ant un programme spe&#x0301;cifique a&#x0300; la re&#x0301;habilitation des logements en Outremer, les re&#x0301;dacteurs de cet amendement entendent re&#x0301;pondre a&#x0300; enjeu double : loger dignement nos concitoyens ultramarins et ame&#x0301;nager efficacement le territoire en utilisant le ba&#x0302;ti existant, dans un contexte de rare&#x0301;faction des terres constructibles en lien notamment avec la trajectoire ZAN.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-29", "datePublication": "2024-11-15", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Tomb\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-04T22:02:56+01:00", "sort": "Tomb\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N002234?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"codeLoi": "7", "divisionCodeLoi": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}